main event: A report from April 3, 1966, details sightings of unidentified aerial objects in Madison, Wisconsin.
interesting points: The report includes 5 black-and-white photographs of unidentified objects in the sky.,One photograph features a crescent-shaped object which may be a partially illuminated moon.,Multiple images display grainy and indistinct UFO phenomena.,The sightings occurred during nighttime, enhancing the mystery of the observed objects.,The report is classified under the Foreign Technology Division.
